		<div>ok i was rome and greace was on the continet with me and was also fairly large so i declared was on them, mind you its 1990 <br />
so are army's where huge in size so i sign with korea and japan <br />
and greece signs with the mongols and china. BOOOM!!! nukes sent my way and only 1 get through and hits my capitol rome and some other city i forget, heh luckly SDI was there to minimize dmg. hehehe here comes the fun part you use nukes i use nuke sorta fun ;) i had like 40 ICBM's and i i had nuke subs with a nuke near evry single AI capitol MWHAHAHHA i use the subs nukes to hit them, then i use my ICBMs so destroy metropolis's and lux and resource's  i nuked greece so bad that i felt confident i could send in my MA's and raze evry city they had, i win by spaceship launch. <br />
