		<div>:mad: I am America (little 25 ICBMs) and was in a war against Germany (33 ICBMs) :(  and they were on a small island and had 90 panzers and 25 modern armor. they made the mistake of grouping most of their units in one spot.  I might also add that they had the second biggest navy (10 Battleships, 20 subs, 40 AEGIS crusiers, 22 nuclear subs, 20-30 destroyers, and 40 Man-o-War [don't ask) but thats not that hard to do when hardly anyone else had a navy.  13 civs against it including me and 3 nations against us.  I nuked their army wiping it out almost completly, but I broke from normal rutuine and hadn't posted troop carriers off their coast (1 with Marines, 10 with Modern armor) that off course turned out to be a mistake because I thought I had the SDI defense, the next turn 20 cities were nuked destroying most of my army and navy (-30 destroyers out of 47 and 3 carriers out of 30, losing about 12 bombers and 20 fighters no joke thats really what I lost for navy army is a ?):mad: :mad: :mad:  I of course made peace with them because they had 25 tact nukes and I didn't want to find those bobing the few citys I had near by(on another conten.) and to re build my army and navy and air force. luckly they left my trans port ships alone and I have sent them to Germany.  War currently on going.  Of course France also launched nukes at Germany so their weak.</div>
