		<div>I once had a world war that lsated about 300 years. It all started with the damn Russians sneak attacking me. I quickly got my neighbors and friends, France and the Celts, (I was Greece) into alliances. <br />
<br />
We were stomping the Reds with no problem, but teh French and Celts both brought in more allies with Military Alliance and MPP's. Anyway, the Russkies were toast, but before their last city was finished, some dumbass declared war on France, bringing in some of my allies against my other allies, as i struggled to remain neutral.<br />
<br />
Anyway, pretty soon Civs on the other end of the world started declaring war on France, then Germany declared War on Rome. And England declared war on Carthage, and China and Spain declared war on everyone. And the Celts (Who were my friends) declared war on me. And the thing is, just DIDN'T stop.<br />
<br />
Some Civs would make peace, but would IMMEDIATELY declare war on some other Civ. It was madness! &quot;Germany and Rome have made peace.&quot; &quot;The Romans declared war on the Carthaginians!&quot; &quot;The English declared war on the Romans!&quot; &quot;Spain declared war on the Carthaginians!&quot; &quot;Germany declared war on France!&quot;<br />
<br />
 I eventuall got out of all my agreements i had signed, and let the battles rage all around me. Like, 4 Civs were wiped out in the course of the whole thing, and eventually i built the U.N. and my only other candidate was Spain, who had attacked just about everyone, and i won in a landslide :D</div>
